quote.summary: Shanghai Jiaoda Withub Information Industrial Co Ltd is a China-based company mainly engaged in software and information technology (IT) services. The Company's businesses include computer network and internet security integration, application software development, building intelligent system integration as well as IT products sales agent, and others. The Company operates through two segments. The Business Application Solutions and Application Software segment is mainly engaged in the development and provision of business application project service, including business solution, application software, installation and maintenance and data security products. The Sales Products segment is mainly engaged in sales of computers and electronic products and accessories. The Company mainly conducts businesses in the domestic market of China.
